hat summarizes the details of your floorplan account will be sent to this email {!Opportunity.Capital_Account_Rep__c}. Please confirm {!Opportunity.Capital_Account_Rep__c} is the email you want to use for statements and payment reminders. If you wish to send these email updates to another email address, reply to this email with the account you would prefer to use.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">ACV is always looking to improve our user experience and we are excited to share that ACV Capital will soon have an innovative and user-friendly portal that will allow you to access the details of your floorplan at any time. Please look for this exciting announcement in the near future.&nbsp; In the meantime, please reference the attached document to view an example of how to make a payment on your account.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Thank you again for entrusting ACV Capital with your floor plan needs.</font></div>]]></td>
